#: ui/main.qml:28
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Legacy X11 apps with global shortcuts and other features accessed while "
"running in the background need to be able to listen for keystrokes all the "
"time.<nl/><nl/>If you use any of these apps, you can choose your preferred "
"balance of security and compatibility here."
msgstr ""
"Starejše aplikacije X11 z globalnimi bližnjicami in drugimi funkcijami, do "
"katerih dostopate med delovanjem v ozadju, morajo imeti možnost ves čas "
"poslušati pritiske tipk.<nl/><nl/>Če uporabljate katero od teh aplikacij, "
"lahko tukaj izberete želeno ravnovesje med varnostjo in združljivostjo."

#: ui/main.qml:49
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Listening for keystrokes:"
msgstr "Poslušanje pritiskov tipk:"

#: ui/main.qml:52
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is prohibited"
msgid "Prohibited"
msgstr "Prepovedano"

#: ui/main.qml:61
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid "Most secure; global shortcuts will not work in X11 apps"
msgstr "Najbolj varno; globalne bližnjice ne bodo delovale v aplikacijah X11"

#: ui/main.qml:67
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is allowed for…"
msgid "Only the Meta, Control, Alt, and Shift keys"
msgstr "Samo tipke Meta, kontrolka, Alt in dvigalka"

#: ui/main.qml:76
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"High security; push-to-talk and other modifier-only global shortcuts will "
"work in X11 apps"
msgstr ""
"Visoka varnost; bližnjice za pritisni in govori ter druge globalne "
"bližnjice, ki jih je mogoče uporabljati samo za modifikatorje, bodo delovale "
"v aplikacijah X11"

#: ui/main.qml:81
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is allowed for…"
msgid ""
"As above, plus any key pressed while the Control, Alt, or Meta key is also "
"pressed"
msgstr ""
"Kot zgoraj in katerikoli pritisnjena tipka s hkratnim pritiskom tipke "
"Control, Alt ali Meta"

#: ui/main.qml:90
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid "Moderate security; all global shortcuts will work in X11 apps"
msgstr "Zmerna varnost; vse globalne bližnjice bodo delovale v aplikacijah X11"

#: ui/main.qml:96
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is always allowed"
msgid "Always allowed"
msgstr "Vedno dovoljeno"

#: ui/main.qml:105
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Least secure; all X11 apps will be able to see any text you type into any "
"application"
msgstr ""
"Najmanj varno; vse aplikacije X11 bodo lahko videle katero koli besedilo, ki "
"ga vnesete v katero koli aplikacijo"

#: ui/main.qml:111
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Note that using this setting will reduce system security and permit "
"malicious software to steal passwords and spy on the text that you type. "
"Make sure you understand and accept this risk."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da bo ta nastavitev zmanjšala varnost sistema seje X11, ker "
"dovoljuje zlonamernim programom krajo gesel in vohunjenje za besedilom, ki "
"ga tipkate. Prepričajte se, da razumete in sprejemate to tveganje."

#: ui/main.qml:118
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Listening for mouse buttons:"
msgstr "Poslušanje miškinih gumbov:"

#: ui/main.qml:121
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for mouse buttons is allowed"
msgid "Allowed"
msgstr "Dovoljeno"

#: ui/main.qml:130
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Moderate security; global shortcuts involving mouse buttons will work in X11 "
"apps"
msgstr ""
"Zmerna varnost; globalne bližnjice z gumbi miške bodo delovale v aplikacijah "
"X11"

#: ui/main.qml:141
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Control of pointer and keyboard:"
msgstr "Kontrola kazalca in tipkovnice:"

#: ui/main.qml:146
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@option:check Allowed control of pointer and keyboard without asking for "
"permissions for allowed apps"
msgid "Allowed apps"
msgstr "Dovoljene aplikacije"

#: ui/main.qml:152
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "See Allowed Applications…"
msgstr "Glejte dovoljene aplikacije…"

#: ui/main.qml:163
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Moderate security; XWayland-using apps claiming to be something on this list "
"will be able to take control of the computer, because XWayland-using apps’ "
"identities can’t be verified"
msgstr ""
"Zmerna varnost; Aplikacije, ki uporabljajo XWayland in trdijo, da so na tem "
"seznamu, bodo lahko prevzele nadzor nad računalnikom, ker identitet "
"aplikacij, ki uporabljajo XWayland, ni mogoče preveriti."

#: ui/main.qml:169
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@option:radio Allow control of pointer and keyboard without asking for "
"permission"
msgid "Allow without asking for permission"
msgstr "Dovoli brez prošnje za dovoljenje"

#: ui/main.qml:174
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid "Least secure; all X11 apps will be able to take control of the computer"
msgstr ""
"Najmanj varno; vse aplikacije X11 bodo lahko prevzele nadzor nad računalnikom"

#: ui/main.qml:181
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Note that using this setting will drastically reduce system security and "
"permit malicious software to take complete control of your pointer and "
"keyboard. Make sure you understand and accept this risk."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da bo uporaba te nastavitve drastično zmanjšala varnost sistema "
"in zlonamerni programski opremi omogočila popoln nadzor nad vašim kazalcem "
"in tipkovnico. Prepričajte se, da razumete in sprejemate to tveganje."

#: ui/main.qml:189
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@title:window title of the page opened by the 'See allowed applications' "
"button"
msgid "Applications allowed to control the pointer and keyboard"
msgstr "Aplikacije, ki lahko upravljajo kazalec in tipkovnico"

#: ui/main.qml:209
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip %1 is the name of the app/binary"
msgid "Do not allow %1 to control the pointer and keyboard without asking"
msgstr "Ne dovoli %1, da upravlja kazalec in tipkovnico brez vprašanja"

